- HOW'S "PISTOL PETE"
TREATING HIM?

13:05.430 --> 13:09.196
- PETE IS WORKING HIM
LATE NIGHTS.

13:09.300 --> 13:13.054
- SHE'S A SLAVE DRIVER.
- SHE'S KEEPING HIM ON HIS TOES.

13:13.170 --> 13:15.331
IT'S GOOD.
- THAT'S AN AMAZING OPPORTUNITY.

13:15.440 --> 13:16.680
- IT'S AMAZING FOR HIM.

13:16.790 --> 13:19.998
FOR US, YOU KNOW.
- OH, YEAH, YEAH.

13:20.100 --> 13:21.374
- OH, MY GOD.
I'M CHEWING.

13:21.490 --> 13:23.208
- ALL RIGHT, MAX. NO MORE
PICTURES OF AUNT SARAH, MAX.

13:23.310 --> 13:25.005
- HANK HAS A HUGE PICTURE
OF AUNT SARAH

13:25.110 --> 13:26.031
THAT HE KEEPS IN HIS DRAWER.

13:26.150 --> 13:27.219
- OKAY.
- WHAT?

13:27.320 --> 13:28.719
- WHAT?
- WHAT--WHAT'D YOU SAY?

13:28.840 --> 13:30.558
- HOW DRESSED IS SHE
IN THIS...

13:30.670 --> 13:31.762
- IT'S BECAUSE HE LIKED YOU,

13:31.880 --> 13:33.188
BUT HE SAYS HE DOESN'T
LIKE YOU ANYMORE

13:33.290 --> 13:34.564
BECAUSE YOU'RE FLAKY,
AND YOU HAVE BAGGAGE.

13:34.670 --> 13:36.524
- BUDDY, THAT IS NOT APPROPRIATE
TALK AT THE DINNER TABLE.

13:36.640 --> 13:39.017
- MAX, THAT'S PERSONAL.
- HANK TOLD YOU I HAVE BAGGAGE?

13:39.120 --> 13:41.054
EXCUSE ME.
I HAVE BAGGAGE?

13:41.160 --> 13:42.570
WHO HAS BAGGAGE IN
THAT SCENARIO?

13:42.680 --> 13:44.398
- AND HE SAYS THAT
YOU SHOULDN'T MARRY SOMEONE

13:44.510 --> 13:46.330
WHO HAS BAGGAGE BECAUSE
THEY'RE FILLED WITH PAIN.

13:46.440 --> 13:47.543
- I'M SO SORRY.
- MAX, THAT'S ALL.

13:47.650 --> 13:48.810
WE'RE DONE.

13:48.930 --> 13:51.239
- FIRST OF ALL,
ARE WE HAVING THIS CONVERSATION?

13:51.340 --> 13:52.614
- THIS IS THE GREATEST
CONVERSATION

13:52.720 --> 13:53.994
WE'VE HAD IN MONTHS.

13:54.100 --> 13:54.998
I'M SORRY
THAT THE BABY'S MISSING IT.

13:55.110 --> 13:56.270
- WHY AM I TALKING?

13:56.380 --> 13:58.348
- ALSO, HANK AND I
ARE BEST FRIENDS TOO.

13:58.450 --> 13:59.439
- YOU'RE BEST FRIENDS?

13:59.560 --> 14:01.380
- YEAH, I SPEND MORE TIME
WITH HIM AFTER SCHOOL,

14:01.490 --> 14:03.412
THAN ANY ONE PERSON IN SCHOOL,
AND I'M HIS ONLY FRIEND,

14:03.530 --> 14:04.383
WHICH MAKES US BEST FRIENDS.

14:04.490 --> 14:05.730
- HONEY, I'M SURE HANK
HAS OTHER FRIENDS.

14:05.840 --> 14:07.216
- ACTUALLY, HE DOESN'T.

14:07.320 --> 14:09.595
- HE ALSO CALLS ME A WEIRD
NICKNAME CALLED "MAD MAX."

14:09.710 --> 14:11.462
